  <description type="morphology">Caudices to 10 dm × 2–6(–8) cm.  Rosette leaf blades whitish or sometimes green, triangular-lanceolate, 6–25 × 1–3 cm, surfaces usually farinose.  Inflorescences: floral shoots 2–7 dm × 5–15 mm; cyme often ± cylindric; branches 1–3 times bifurcate; cincinni mostly 3–8-flowered, mostly 1–5 cm.  Corollas 14–23 mm diam.  2n = 34.</description>
